  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposals by reason of unsatisfactory layout resulting in the absence of windows to the main communal spaces of the property, specifically the kitchen, would create a poor standard of internal environment for occupiers of the C4 HMO. The proposal would therefore be contrary to polices DM D2 of the Sites and Policies Plan 2014, and policies CS 8, CS9 and CS14 within the Council's Adopted Core Strategy 2011.",
    "Reason : 2 - In the absence of sufficient information confirming the use of the manager's office, the council are unable to ascertain the impact on neighbour amenity. It is therefore concluded that the proposal would fail to comply with the principles of policy D3 of the London Plan 2021 and DMD2 of the Sites and Policies Plan 2014.",
    "Reason : 3 - In the absence of satisfactory and convenient access to cycle storage facilities, the scheme is contrary to the London Plan (2021) Policy T5, Merton's Core Strategy (2011) Policy CS 18 and Merton's Sites and Policies Plan (2014) Policy DM T1"
  ],
